title: Palestinians protest as Nakba Day draws near
text:
Palestinians protest as Nakba Day draws near 5:13pm BST - 01:18
Demonstrators are protesting for the last Friday of a six-week protest at the Gaza-Israel border ahead of the U.S. relocating their embassy from Tel Aviv to Jerusalem. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
